
// This Hyperlambda code creates a scheduled task with a unique identifier [task-id-xyx]. The task logs a message indicating it is the first day of any month at 5 AM UTC. The task is defined using the [tasks.create] slot and the [log.info] slot is used to output the log message. The task is not yet scheduled for execution, but it is ready to be scheduled with a specific pattern or time.
tasks.create:task-id-xyx
   .lambda
      log.info:It is the 1st of the month, any month, and the time is 5AM at night UTC.
